doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Kyle Kochanek's Online Space
        meta(
            name="description"
            content="Kyle's online space for his portfolio and different musing on design and craft."
        )
        meta(name="author" content="Kyle Kochanek")

        link(rel="stylesheet" href="./scss/main.css")

        //- Favicon
        link(rel="icon" href="favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon")

    body
        header
            .container
                .heading-group
                    svg(width="2.5rem" height="2.5rem")
                        circle(cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%" fill="currentColor")
                    h1 I'm Kyle,
                h2.h4 I'm what happens when you merge the #[span.text-creative creative] & #[span.text-logical logical] branches without #[span.text-personality resolving] conflicts.
                p Features include pixel-perfect design, clean code commits, vector illustrations, and an unhealthy obsession with design tokens.

        main
            section.typography-test
                h2 Typography
                    span.italic Test
                    |  Content

                .text-block
                    p This is a paragraph of text. It demonstrates the body copy style. The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. Pack my box with five dozen liquor jugs.
                    p Here's another paragraph to show spacing between paragraphs. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.

                .text-with-heading
                    h3 Section Heading
                    p This shows how a heading looks when paired with body text. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.

                .list-examples
                    h4 List Styles
                    ul
                        li Unordered list item 1
                        li Unordered list item 2
                        li Unordered list item 3
                    ol
                        li Ordered list item 1
                        li Ordered list item 2
                        li Ordered list item 3

                .quote-block
                    blockquote "This is a blockquote. It can be used to highlight important text or quotations from other sources."
                    cite - Citation Example

                .text-emphasis
                    p This paragraph contains
                        em emphasized text
                        |  and
                        strong strong text
                        |  to show how inline styles appear.

                .link-styles
                    p Here's an example of a
                        a(href="#") link style
                        |  within a paragraph of text.

                .text-sizes
                    p.text-small This is small text.
                    p.text-large This is large text.
                    p.text-xl This is extra large text.

        //- Include footer
        include components/footer

        //- JavaScript
        script.
            // Add your custom scripts here